it.emarolab.scene_identification_tracking.semanticSceneLibrary.objects

Class Semantics.ReadingOutcome<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.emarolab.scene_identification_tracking.semanticSceneLibrary.objects.Semantics.ReadingOutcome<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of the read buffer.
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    MORDescriptor.ReadingOutcome
    Enclosing interface:
    Semantics

    public static class Semantics.ReadingOutcome<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    A container for reading results.

    In particular, it contains:

    • the read buffer (of generic type 'T') for accessing data,
    • the Semantics.ReadingState, describing the state associated to the buffer.
    File: it.emarolab.scene_identification_tracking.semanticSceneLibrary.objects.Semantics
